ABOUT US
ENJOY OUR WONDERFUL OCEAN VIEW, AND OUR DELICIOUS FOOD!
There's no other place like us!
We are so proud to say that we are Homestead's newest beachfront sport bar getaway restaurant. La Playa Grill Seafood & Bar is a beach view restaurant located in Homestead, in Bayfront Park and Marina, or better known as the Herbert Hoover Marina.  La Playa Grill’s varied menu is seafood focused and sports bar. We are conveniently located a few miles from the city of Miami. We are ten minutes east of South Dixie Highway, off to the right inside Homestead Bayfront Park. Our nautical casual family atmosphere makes La Playa Grill perfect for a getaway with your friends, family, corporate events and special events.  La Playa Grill is perfect for hosting parties. La Playa Grill offers a beautiful relaxing waterside experience with indoor and outdoor seating. Our menu features fried calamari, lobster, shrimp, Mahi-mahi, Hamburgers, Chicken wings, Children’s menu, and other delicious options. Our drink selections include the coldest beer in town and homemade cocktails. We also have live music every weekend and amazing happy hour specials. Call us for additional information, we guarantee you that will love La Playa Grill Seafood & Bar!
